Class Helpers

    • kWL.Helpers

  • public class Helpers
extends java.lang.Object
    Helpers is a class of static helper methods of various utility. Currently, I am considering moving some of the methods from here to the Representation class.

      • copyAndAdd

        public static int[] copyAndAdd(int[] array,
                               int elementToAdd)
        Copies an integer array to a new array of size = the original array's size + 1. The new integer array additionally has a new a integer added at the last index and the integer element is given as an argument. The method is used in kWLClass when extending generation sequences.
        Parameters:
        elementToAdd - an int which is the element added at the last index of the new array.
        Returns:
        int[] an integer array.
